text: Sandnes Idrettslag is a Norwegian sports club from Sandnes, founded in 1946. The club has sections for track and field athletics, orienteering and skiing. Athletes competing for Sandnes IL include Henrik Ingebrigtsen, Bjørnar Ustad Kristensen, Filip Ingebrigtsen, Lars Vikan Rise, Per Magne Florvaag, Marius Bakken Støle, and Jakob Ingebrigtsen. ==References== == External links == * Category:Sports clubs established in 1946 Category:Sandnes Category:Orienteering clubs in Norway Category:Athletics clubs in Norway Category:1946 establishments in Norway
